From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: robert-brunson-fragile <siinspam@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 23:52:21 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 13/13] fix(session): preserve runtime metadata and archive
 state

Persist safe runtime model/provider metadata on API-created sessions so future turns restore the actual Hermes runtime instead of the advertised API model id.

Also keep desktop archived/deleted sessions hidden across stale refreshes and replace transient loading indicators with quieter session UI states.

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

